### GET all galleries
GET http://localhost:3000/api/gallery
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST new gallery with multiple files
POST http://localhost:3000/api/gallery
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Science Fair 2025
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Highlights from the annual science fair
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

ART
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="department"

SCIENCES
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="science1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads/science1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="science2.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./uploads/science2.mp4
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### GET single gallery (replace :id with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/gallery/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

